    <description>Microsoft Windows AI Machine Learning APIs. This package provides the Windows ML runtime, ONNX Runtime integration, and DirectML support for Windows desktop applications. Minimum OS: Windows 10 19H1 (Build 18362) or later. For support down to 17763, install Microsoft.WindowsAppSDK.ML.</description>
